thread.title: Bill Archer
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Bill Archer

author: Bill Archer
title: Bill Archer
text: I sent a two kilogram parcel to the Philippines it cost over $60 that is around the same as Australia post but much faster (2 weeks compared to 6-8 weeks for Australia post) and the recipient did not have to pay for delivery as philpost seem to charge for delivery.
